{"tid":1393562,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"古有狗急跳牆 今有狗急毀連儂牆","createTime":"2019-08-01T06:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T14:36:07.000Z","uid":211565,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"722ee8f7791c717f554256571e296a0578010b03","tid":1393562,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:34:29.000Z","msg":"今朝連續見到好幾個po<br />\n話觀塘、牛頭角、藍田既連儂牆都相繼被破壞<br />\n沙田直頭出埋火燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班廢老一而再再而三咁針對啲poster同memo紙<br />\n可唔可以理解做：<br />\n連儂牆有一定宣傳威力，令佢地好驚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係咁就更加要繼續貼，每日更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">sorry for 1999</span>"},{"pid":"0e02ef503dbeb712ff4bbb3c7cf3b0e6bc782c61","tid":1393562,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:47:01.000Z","msg":"用鎖頭！<br />\n<br />\nE.g. 喺尖東海傍建立一個「連儂海傍」景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等大陸人打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ApM28As.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FApM28As.png&h=00b9d1fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/APRFVfu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAPRFVfu.png&h=6c611bda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FkyXYkA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFkyXYkA.png&h=7dfc92f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[永久連儂牆］點解唔用鎖頭？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1393906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1393906</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"de90f3e9b645929b7e79